00:16:49.210 --> 00:16:53.879
>> Jason Thorpe: So we also have a new
data layout for streaming workloads.

00:16:53.879 --> 00:16:58.529
We're going to talk about that just a bit more
here in a second with a little diagram.

00:16:58.529 --> 00:17:03.620
But we think that this is going to be really
good for folks that are making the transition

00:17:03.620 --> 00:17:09.390
to uncompressed high def video, want to work
