00:37:10.980 --> 00:37:16.809
And that allows them to connect
these autodesk work stations to Xsan

00:37:16.809 --> 00:37:22.460
and allow Final Cut Pro to be a
feeder into those work stations.

00:37:22.460 --> 00:37:28.559
Those are incredibly expensive work stations
